Below is the entire Museum Upgrading Script

This is an auto-upgrading gem script for the museum, to use it you need 13 lines. Just set what your max buy will be in the Museum_Auto_Buyer then press m while in the museum and let it roll. Use https://github.com/Xenos6666/TPT2_scripts/tree/modular_V2/common/execution_stack with it to save yourself hours. Place the gems you will upgrade into your equipped area, all gems in the inventory area on the right will be deleted on script start.
